trans-unit.source: Represents a dictionary that contains xmlns mappings for XAML namespaces in WPF.
trans-unit.target: 表示包含 WPF 中 XAML 命名空間之 xmlns 對應的字典。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> maps XAML namespace prefixes to the complete XAML namespace URI.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> 將 XAML 命名空間前置詞對應至完整的 XAML 命名空間 URI。

trans-unit.source: For XAML usage in applications and XAML namespaces in general, the URI is often not a schema-style URI that includes `http://`.
trans-unit.target: 在應用程式中的 XAML 用法和一般 XAML 命名空間，URI 通常不是結構描述樣式 URI，包括`http://`。

trans-unit.source: It is instead a user-defined mapping to a CLR namespace and assembly.
trans-unit.target: 而是使用者定義對應的 CLR 命名空間和組件。

trans-unit.source: That assembly contains the backing types being referred to.
trans-unit.target: 組件包含備份類型所參考。

trans-unit.source: For details, see [XAML Namespaces and Namespace Mapping for WPF XAML](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/xaml-namespaces-and-namespace-mapping-for-wpf-xaml.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[XAML 命名空間和 WPF XAML 命名空間對應](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/xaml-namespaces-and-namespace-mapping-for-wpf-xaml.md)。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> adds the concept of scope for a XAML namespace.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>將 XAML 命名空間範圍的概念。

trans-unit.source: A default <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> might contain prefix keys and XML namespace URI values.
trans-unit.target: 預設值<xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>可能包含前置詞索引鍵和 XML 命名空間 URI 值。

trans-unit.source: The scope concept in <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> parallels the XML concept that a prefix might be redefined.
trans-unit.target: 中的範圍概念<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>平行設計可能會重新定義前置詞的 XML 概念。

trans-unit.source: If so, the redefinition only applies at that level or below in a DOM view of the XML (the previous definition applies at higher level in the DOM).
trans-unit.target: 若是如此，重新定義僅適用於層級或以下版本 （先前的定義適用於在 DOM 中的更高層級） 的 xml DOM 檢視中。

trans-unit.source: The scope concept is mostly abstracted away in the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> API, such that you can call APIs such as <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary.LookupNamespace%2A> without being concerned about scope.
trans-unit.target: 範圍概念大部分抽象中<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>應用程式開發介面，例如，您可以呼叫 Api 例如<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary.LookupNamespace%2A>而不用擔心範圍。

trans-unit.source: However, <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> does expose <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary.PushScope%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary.PopScope%2A> so that a custom <xref:System.Windows.Markup.ParserContext> implementation that changes scope can synchronize with the scope for the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: 不過，<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>沒有公開<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary.PushScope%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary.PopScope%2A>，讓自訂<xref:System.Windows.Markup.ParserContext>變更範圍的實作可以同步處理的範圍與<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>。

trans-unit.source: Locks the dictionary so that it cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: 鎖定字典，以便無法對其進行變更。

trans-unit.source: This must be done before setting the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> to a property (typically on a <xref:System.Windows.Markup.ParserContext>).
trans-unit.target: 這必須完成，才能設定<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>屬性 (通常在<xref:System.Windows.Markup.ParserContext>)。

trans-unit.source: Attempting to modify the dictionary after the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary> is sealed throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 嘗試修改後的字典<xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlnsDictionary>密封格式，則會擲回<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。
